<br>
I think the runes should drop in dungeon zones appropriate to the expansion was introduced in.  For Kunark era spells:  Sebilis, Howling Stones, Skyfire, Karnors Castle (low end 50's spells).  For Velious make it Velks and Dragon Necropolis.  For Luclin:  Akevan Ruins, Greig's End (can't think of more at the moment).<br>
<br>
Bottom line is spell research is useless in its current form.  Because the people who need the spells can't get to them in their current form.  I believe the only one who have benefited from this are the 65th level people that hunt in the PoP zones where the runes drop now.  They then turn around and sell them for outrageous amounts of money.  Basically no change as before.<br>
<br>
